OL,3,CUtility bills and tax hikes drive
OL,4,Cinflation higher
OL,6,FAll the arrows are pointing in the
OL,7,Fwrong direction.
OL,9,FInflation rose significantly in April
OL,10,Fon every measure, as prices increased
OL,11,Fmore rapidly across the UK economy.
OL,13,FThe headline annual rate jumped to
OL,14,F3.5%, above the 3.3% economists
OL,15,Fexpected and higher than the 3.4%
OL,16,Fforecast by the Bank of England.
OL,18,FThe rise was driven by higher food and
OL,19,Fenergy prices, but core inflation `
OL,20,Fwhich strips out both ` also climbed,
OL,21,Freaching 3.8% last month.
