OL,3,CUtility bills and tax hikes drive
OL,4,Cinflation higher
OL,6,FInflation in the services sector,
OL,7,Fwhich the Bank monitors closely as a
OL,8,Fguide to domestic price pressures,
OL,9,Fincreased to 5.4% ` a clear signal
OL,10,Fthat wage growth is strong, broad-
OL,11,Fbased, and persistent.
OL,13,FThat might sound like good news. But
OL,14,Fthe Bank worries that firms are
OL,15,Fcovering the cost of higher wages by
OL,16,Fraising prices ` fueling a fresh round
OL,17,Fof inflation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
