OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWe knew energy and water bills would
OL,12,Frise sharply last month, so a rebound
OL,13,Fin inflation wasn't a surprise. But
OL,14,Fthe key question now is why the
OL,15,Frebound was bigger than expected and
OL,16,Fwhether it will last.
OL,18,F"This was more than an energy and
OL,19,Fwater story," says Paul Dales at
OL,20,FCapital Economics.
