OL,3,CUtility bills and tax hikes drive
OL,4,Cinflation higher
OL,6,FThe Chancellor says she is
OL,7,F"disappointed" by the latest inflation
OL,8,Fdata and acknowledges that "cost-of-
OL,9,Fliving pressures are still weighing
OL,10,Fdown on working people."
OL,12,FEnergy bills are the biggest upward
OL,13,Fforce but that pressure may ease soon.
OL,14,FOil prices have fallen significantly
OL,15,Fsince President Trump started his
OL,16,Ftariff war in earnest. Anyone with a
OL,17,Fcar has likely felt the effect at the
OL,18,Fpump.
