OL,3,CUtility bills and tax hikes drive
OL,4,Cinflation higher
OL,6,FStill, a second wave of inflation is
OL,7,Fbuffeting the UK. There's no
OL,8,Fexpectation prices will take off in
OL,9,Fthe way the did from July 2021, but
OL,10,Fthe Bank thinks headline inflation
OL,11,Fwill stay above 3% for several months,
OL,12,Fpeaking at 3.7% in the autumn before
OL,13,Fgradually easing.
OL,15,FThat will be uncomfortable for many
OL,16,Fhouseholds and painful for those on
OL,17,Fthe lowest incomes.
